নবজীবনের যাত্রাপথে দাও দাও এই বর\n:
Give this boon on the journey of new life
            Oh Hryadeshvara--
    Fill the wealth of love and direct your heart;
As if in the midst of this world, the south face is the king;
In the form of happiness I receive alms, in the form of sorrow I receive initiation;
May the mind be free from pettiness, united with the Absolute,
      Good work does not mean fatigue
          peace peace peace
